Ranges used to create a library files, e.g.

{ "TargetTemp": ControlRange(min,max,step) , "Exposure": ControlRange(min,max,step)  }

If the file has been created by fusing other files, then this is a list, e.g.
[
  { "TargetTemp": ControlRange(min,max,step) , "Exposure": ControlRange(min,max,step)  },
  { "TargetTemp": ControlRange(min,max,step) , "Exposure": ControlRange(min,max,step)  }
]
